docker run -v /home/...../src/contracts:/sources ethereum/solc:0.6.2 -o /sources --abi --bin /sources/UPCGoldBank.sol

the sources directory needs to be specified as the output or no abis or bins are being created on local.



build wrappers like:

epirus generate solidity generate --abiFile=/home/tenten/Projects/upc-wallet/contracts/upcgold/wrappers/UPCGoldBank.abi --outputDir=/home/tenten/output --package=upcgold
